rows.label: qst201608_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, friends choose right moment to
stop by! Timing is impeccable, meh!

rows.label: qst201608_msg0003
rows.name:
Pi lined up next gig!
This time, friend Nanakoori play in
Bajena Playhouse in Invidia.

rows.label: qst201608_msg0004
rows.name: ...I'm going to play in the playhouse?!

rows.label: qst201608_msg0005
rows.name:
Hah, that's awesome.
Nice one, Nanakoori!

rows.label: qst201608_msg0006
rows.name:
That playhouse of old man Cole
now suppose to be much bigger
than before.

rows.label: qst201608_msg0008
rows.name:
Nanakoori, you've worked hard for this.
Take it as an acknowledgment of
your effort!

rows.label: qst201608_msg0012
rows.name:
Well then, Pi go ahead to seal
deal!

rows.label: qst201608_msg0013
rows.name:
Friend Nanakoori, make show
that be remembered for ages!

rows.label: qst201608_msg0015
rows.name:
You'd better make sure you're ready,
Nanakoori!

rows.label: qst201608_msg0016
rows.name:
Yeah... I'm a little apprehensive, but...
I have to see it through...

rows.label: qst201608_msg0017
rows.name:
Friend should bring Nanakoori here.
Have important thing to tell!
